{"tid":1516533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"銅鑼灣有四架狗車","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:16.000Z","uid":64845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"491f429e8fe91143bda32f54bc117eb5030e9f1e","tid":1516533,"uid":64845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"有無人知發生咩事？<br />\n見到有兩隻狗上咗樓<br />\n一堆傾緊野"},{"pid":"adf60e865aa10c17e30c69f641fccb29fdf7053a","tid":1516533,"uid":19743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人撐香港隊<br />\n入場向世界表達訴求<br />\n賽前有奏鄰國國歌儀式，大家識做!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC7JUxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC7JUxG.png&h=4352d932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BKDZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BKDZn.png&h=fd2e6806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQHFcjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQHFcjE.jpg&h=6cb0627d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHDpEVO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHDpEVO.jpg&h=cd36f349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地仲可以用香港隊名義踢國際賽係因為我地同中國足協係完全分開運作<br />\n有自己既地方聯賽<br />\n如果可以既話<br />\n希望咁多位可以多多支持香港超級足球聯賽<br />\n因為香港足總成日話港超無出路<br />\n要返中國聯賽/大灣區聯賽"},{"pid":"81d746aae0cfff6ce59285872551b638e75740df","tid":1516533,"uid":231818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"b731cb01e95d5812481606c4045e46e59878c1e2","tid":1516533,"uid":64845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"啲狗上咗幾棟丈廈"},{"pid":"7c09edd2d33632bfa3d7caacc4118b4abe6986e0","tid":1516533,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"又點啊"},{"pid":"d2eef4e204fbbbe33d6a235c1825f06dbf2ba0a6","tid":1516533,"uid":227673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣邊頭？"},{"pid":"e1925b232a3175eeb9d4319b890fc3bb02cd3703","tid":1516533,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"5943a7c50a769811e540abe47310e9cee3d6e56f","tid":1516533,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daf9c0925cee58f29eba4d9d6fa8ea69608d7fc","tid":1516533,"uid":64845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2eef4e204fbbbe33d6a235c1825f06dbf2ba0a6","tid":1516533,"uid":227673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣邊頭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"老虎堂個條街"},{"pid":"fa16bfcd65be205e3576ecb77867f13903c2f737","tid":1516533,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"都無示威，搵鬼傾咩"}]}